item.title: Game Shark Killer 3
item.description: The game Shark Killer 3 presents you with a powerful marine predator, which has no equal in the ocean in terms of bloodthirstiness. But today people have learned to resist these monsters. Therefore, you need to play carefully. By controlling a shark, you can eat everything around, but you should beware of fishing schooners that throw nets and even dynamite into the sea.
